OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright but breezy day with a
OL,6,Fmix of sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,7,FThe showers most frequent across the
OL,8,Fnorth, with a risk of hail and thunder
OL,9,Fhere. Clouding over with some rain
OL,10,Farriving by dusk in the far northwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA band of rain and strong
OL,13,Fwinds in the far northwest will move
OL,14,Fslowly southeastwards overnight,
OL,15,Freaching northern England by dawn.
OL,16,FLargely dry ahead of it, with some
OL,17,Fclear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
