OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain and strong winds
OL,6,Fcontinuing to move southeastwards
OL,7,Fduring Thursday. Still some sunshine
OL,8,Fahead of this, with bright spells and
OL,9,Fshowers following. Feeling colder
OL,10,Flater in the north.
